body.name: RX-580 Graphics Card, 8GB GDDR5 256BIT Low Noise Desktop PC Gaming Video Card, PCIE 3.0 16X, Dual Cooling Fan, Supports for DirectX 12
body.stockDetail: Only 7 left in stock - order soon.
features: 8GB DDR5 RAM: With a core frequency of 1284MHz and a memory frequency of 1750MHz, the RX580 graphics card can effectively meet your needs. System support: for Windows 10, for Windows 11, for Windows Vista, for Linux.

EASY TO INSTALL: PC graphics card with PCI Express 3.0 16X slot, small size, plug and play, easy to install, good performance, easy to carry and store. I/O interface: 1 x HD multimedia interface interface, 1 x DVI interface, 3 x Displayport interface.

STABLE AND DURABLE: Full solid state capacitors, integrated thickened heat sink module, and reinforced PCB material for more stable gaming and working performance. Maximum resolution up to 7680X4320, DirectX 12 support, 6pin or external power supply required.

OUTSTANDING PC PERFORMANCE: If you want a desktop computer and want to play a variety of large games, then this graphics card is probably one of the best choices for general PC work, watching movies and making videos.

EFFICIENT AND QUIET: This gaming graphics card comes with 8GB of video storage capacity and comes with independent cooling dual fans for lower operating temperatures, higher efficiency, low noise and quiet operation.
